<section id="why-us" aria-labelledby="why-us-heading" class="py-16 md:py-24">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4">
    <h2
      id="why-us-heading"
      class="text-[22px] md:text-[28px] font-semibold leading-tight tracking-[-0.01em] text-text-primary mb-4 text-center"
    >
      Why Apex Code
    </h2>
    <p class="text-base font-normal leading-relaxed text-text-muted text-center mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Two founders. No account managers. You work directly with the people building your product.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16">
      <div class="text-center px-4">
        <p class="text-base font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">Human Touch</p>
        <p class="text-sm font-normal leading-relaxed text-text-muted">
          Direct access to the founders who built your solution — no tickets, no handoffs, no delays.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center px-4">
        <p class="text-base font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">Fast Delivery</p>
        <p class="text-sm font-normal leading-relaxed text-text-muted">
          We scope tightly and ship in weeks, not quarters. You see working software early and often.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center px-4">
        <p class="text-base font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">Modern Stack</p>
        <p class="text-sm font-normal leading-relaxed text-text-muted">
          We use current tools — AI APIs, TypeScript, cloud-native infrastructure — so your solution doesn't age out.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-surface-raised border border-border rounded-md p-6">
        <p class="text-base font-semibold text-text-primary mb-3">[Founder Name 1]</p>
        <p class="text-sm font-normal leading-relaxed text-text-muted">
          Full-stack developer with deep experience in AI integration and backend systems.
          Obsessed with building things that actually work in production, not just in demos.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-surface-raised border border-border rounded-md p-6">
        <p class="text-base font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">[Founder Name 2]</p>
        <p class="text-sm font-normal leading-relaxed text-text-muted">
          Product-minded engineer who bridges the gap between what clients need and what
          gets built. Focused on shipping fast without cutting corners.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
